miliar with the basic tasks and technologies in the field of natural langua=
ge processing, including but not limited to text classification, sentiment =
analysis, machine translation, question answering systems, etc. Have good a=
lgorithm design and programming abilities, conduct efficient code optimizat=
ion and debugging, master data structure and algorithm design, and be famil=
iar with common machine learning algorithms and tools.</p></li><li><p>Proje=
ct Experience: Be able to independently undertake the design and implementa=
